#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter addresses a number of issues that frequently cause confusion, "
"especially for new users of &kmymoney;. If you find that &kmymoney; is doing "
"something you don't understand (or sometimes not doing something you want it "
"to do,) please check this list before asking for help on one of the mailing "
"lists. If your problem is not mentioned here, refer to the section on <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">getting help</link>."
msgstr ""
"To poglavje obravnava številna vprašanja, ki pogosto povzročajo zmedo, "
"zlasti pri novih uporabnikih &kmymoney;. Če najdete, da &kmymoney; počne "
"nekaj, česar ne razumete (ali včasih ne počne nekaj, kar želite), preverite "
"ta seznam, preden zaprosite za pomoč na enem od poštnih seznamov. Če vaša "
"težava ni omenjena tukaj, glejte razdelek o <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact"
"\">pridobivanju pomoči</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation and Startup Questions"
msgstr "Vprašanja glede namestitve in zagona"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmymoney; crashes when I try to launch it."
msgstr "&kmymoney; se sesuje, ko ga poskušam zagnati."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many reasons &kmymoney; might crash or give an error instead of "
"starting up normally. Sometimes an error message is shown, but if not, you "
"can run &kmymoney; from a command line, to see if any useful information is "
"output to the console. On &Linux;, this just means typing \"kmymoney\" in a "
"shell. &macOS; should be similar. On &Windows;, you will need to type the "
"full path to the &kmymoney; executable."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko razlogov, zakaj se &kmymoney; lahko sesuje ali povzroči "
"napako, namesto da bi se normalno zagnal. Včasih se prikaže sporočilo o "
"napaki, če pa ni, lahko zaženete &kmymoney; iz ukazne vrstice, da vidite, "
"ali so v konzolo izpisane koristne informacije. V &Linux;u to pomeni le vnos "
"\"kmymoney\" v lupino. V &macOS; mora biti podobno. V &Windows; boste morali "
"vnesti celotno pot do izvedljive datoteke &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this does not show the cause of the problem, you need to determine if "
"there is an issue with the software or with your data. To do this, you need "
"to <link linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">launch &kmymoney;</link> without "
"opening your data file. If the application starts up, but crashes when you "
"try to load your data file, try loading an older copy of your file. (You did "
"make a backup, didn't you?)"
msgstr ""
"Če to ne pokaže vzroka težave, morate ugotoviti, ali je težava v programski "
"opremi ali v vaših podatkih. Če želite to narediti, morate <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.launch\">zagnati &kmymoney;</link>, ne da bi odprli podatkovno "
"datoteko. Če se aplikacija zažene, vendar se sesuje, ko poskušate naložiti "
"podatkovno datoteko, poskusite naložiti starejšo kopijo datoteke. (Saj ste "
"naredili varnostno kopijo, kajne?)"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kmymoney; crashes on startup without trying to load a data file, there "
"may be a problem with your installation. See the section on <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.contact\">getting help</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če &kmymoney; se ob zagonu sesuje, ne da bi poskusil naložiti podatkovno "
"datoteko, je morda težava z vašo namestitvijo. Oglejte si razdelek o <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">pridobivanju pomoči</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will &kmymoney; work on my X/&ubuntu; desktop? Will &kmymoney; work without "
"a full &kde; desktop?"
msgstr ""
"Bo &kmymoney; deloval na mojem namizju X/&ubuntu;? Bo &kmymoney; deloval "
"brez polnega namizja &kde;?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, &kmymoney; will work without a full &kde; desktop, but you will have to "
"install the basic &kde; libraries first. The easiest way to do this is to "
"use your distribution's package management system, which will handle these "
"requirements automatically. If you are going to install from source, you "
"will probably need development versions of those libraries."
msgstr ""
"Da, &kmymoney; bo deloval brez polnega namizja &kde;, vendar boste morali "
"namestiti osnovni &kde; najprej knjižnice. Najlažji način za to je, da "
"uporabite sistem za upravljanje paketov vaše distribucije, ki bo samodejno "
"obravnaval te zahteve. Če boste nameščali iz izvorne kode, boste verjetno "
"potrebovali razvojne različice teh knjižnic."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration Questions"
msgstr "Vprašanja o konfiguraciji"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can I change the start of the fiscal year, to match my tax year or "
"accounting year?"
msgstr ""
"Ali lahko spremenim začetek proračunskega leta, da se ujema z mojim davčnim "
"ali obračunskim letom?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you can easily set the start of the year in the <link linkend=\"details."
"settings.general.global\">Global Options</link> section of the "
"<guilabel>Configure &kmymoney;</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Da, začetek leta lahko preprosto nastavite v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.general.global\">Globalne možnosti</link> pogovornega "
"okna <guilabel>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account and Transaction Questions"
msgstr "Vprašanja o računu in transakcijah"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I edit a transaction?"
msgstr "Zakaj ne morem urediti transakcije?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You cannot make any changes to a transaction with a date before the opening "
"date of the account it is in. The most common reason for this is importing "
"all the data for an account. If the import file does not contain an opening "
"date for the account, &kmymoney; will use the current date. The way to fix "
"this is to edit the account, and <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit"
"\">change the opening date</link> to be earlier than any transaction in that "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije z datumom pred datumom odprtja računa v katerem je, ne morete "
"spreminjati. Najpogostejši razlog za to je uvoz vseh podatkov za ta račun. "
"Če uvozna datoteka ne vsebuje datuma odprtja računa, bo &kmymoney; uporabil "
"trenutni datum. To lahko popravite tako, da uredite račun in <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.edit\">spremenite datum odprtja</link> tako, da bo pred "
"katerokoli transakcijo v tem računu."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why is a transaction shown in red and how can I get rid of the color?"
msgstr "Zakaj je transakcija prikazana rdeče in kako se lahko znebim te barve?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A transaction is shown in red if any part of the amount has not been "
"assigned to a category. This is most commonly caused by importing a QIF or "
"OFX file or by downloading statement data online. All you have to do is to "
"modify the transaction such that the whole amount of the transaction is "
"assigned to categories."
msgstr ""
"Transakcija je prikazana rdeče, če katerikoli del zneska ni bil dodeljen "
"kategoriji. To je najpogosteje posledica uvoza datoteke QIF ali OFX ali "
"prenosa podatkov izpiskov prek spleta. Vse kar morate storiti je, da "
"spremenite transakcijo tako, da je celoten znesek transakcije dodeljen "
"kategorijam."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I add an opening balance to an account?"
msgstr "Zakaj ne morem dodati začetnega stanja na račun?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you provide an opening balance when you create an account, it is shown as "
"the first transaction for the account. If you do not, then the transaction "
"is not there, and because it is a special type of transaction, you cannot "
"simply add it as you could a deposit or withdrawal. However, you can add it "
"later by <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">editing the account</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če navedete začetno stanje, ko ustvarite račun, je to prikazano kot prva "
"transakcija za ta račun. Če tega ne storite, potem transakcije ni, in ker "
"gre za posebno vrsto transakcije, je ne morete preprosto dodati, kot bi "
"lahko vlogo ali dvig. Vendar jo lahko dodate pozneje, tako da <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.edit\">uredite račun</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I created an account, I used the wrong type, and now it won't let me "
"change it. I can edit the account, but the dropdown for account type is "
"either disabled, or does not list all the possible types."
msgstr ""
"Ko sem ustvaril račun, sem uporabil napačno vrsto in zdaj mi je ne dovoli "
"spremeniti. Račun lahko urejam, vendar je spustni meni za vrsto računa "
"onemogočen ali pa ne navaja vseh možnih vrst."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can easily change an account type between checking, savings, and cash. "
"However, because of the way &kmymoney; stores the account information, it "
"does not allow other changes of account type. The way around this is to "
"<link linkend=\"details.accounts.create\">create a new account of the "
"correct type</link>, move all the transactions from the old to the new "
"account, and then <link linkend=\"details.accounts.delete\"> delete the old "
"account.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Vrsto računa lahko preprosto spremenite med čekovnim, varčevalnim in "
"gotovinskim. Vendar zaradi načina kako &kmymoney; hrani podatke o računu, ne "
"dovoljuje drugih sprememb vrste računa. Temu se izognete tako, da <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.create\">ustvarite nov račun pravilne vrste</"
"link>, premaknete vse transakcije iz starega v nov račun in nato <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.delete\"> izbrišete stari račun.</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have a loan with 0% interest, but I get an error in the New Loan Wizard "
"that does not let me use this value."
msgstr ""
"Imam posojilo z 0 % obrestmi, vendar dobim napako v čarovniku za novo "
"posojilo, ki mi ne dovoljuje uporabe te vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The internal calculations of the new loan wizard do not allow a 0% interest "
"rate. The best way to handle this situation is to <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.create.account\">create a simple liability account</link> with a "
"starting balance for the amount of the loan, and then <link linkend="
"\"details.schedules.new\">create a schedule</link> for the required payments."
msgstr ""
"Interni izračuni čarovnika za nova posojila ne dovoljujejo 0-odstotne "
"obrestne mere. Najboljši način za rešitev te situacije je, da <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.create.account\">ustvarite preprost račun obveznosti</"
"link> z začetnim stanjem za znesek posojila in nato <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules.new\">ustvarite urnik</link> za zahtevana plačila."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why don't I see all my transactions in the ledger?"
msgstr "Zakaj ne vidim vseh svojih transakcij v glavni knjigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several settings that control which transactions are displayed in "
"the Ledger View of an account. First, check the <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.view.filter\">ledger filter area</link>. If there is anything typed "
"in the search box, only transactions containing that text will be shown. If "
"the status dropdown has been changed from <quote>Any status,</quote> then "
"only transaction of the selected type will be shown. In addition, there are "
"two important settings in the <link linkend=\"details.settings.general.filter"
"\">filter options</link> section on the &kmymoney; Settings dialog. If the "
"<guilabel>Do not show transactions prior to</guilabel> field is set, only "
"transactions on or after that date will be shown in the ledger. If the "
"<guilabel>Do not show reconciled transactions</guilabel> box is checked, "
"then no reconciled transactions will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več nastavitev, ki nadzorujejo, katere transakcije so prikazane v "
"pogledu glavne knjige računa. Najprej preverite <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.view.filter\">območje filtra glavne knjige</link>. Če je v iskalno "
"polje karkoli vneseno, bodo prikazane samo transakcije, ki vsebujejo to "
"besedilo. Če je bil spustni meni statusa spremenjen iz <quote>Kateri koli "
"status</quote>, bo prikazana samo transakcija izbrane vrste. Poleg tega sta "
"v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.settings.general.filter\">možnosti "
"filtra</link> na &kmymoney; Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami. Če je nastavljeno "
"polje <guilabel>Ne prikaži transakcij pred</guilabel>, bodo v knjigi "
"prikazane samo transakcije na ali po tem datumu. Če je polje <guilabel>Ne "
"prikaži usklajenih transakcij</guilabel> označeno, potem ne bodo prikazane "
"nobene usklajene transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I mistyped the name of a payee and want to change it in all transaction. Is "
"there a global search/replace?"
msgstr ""
"Napačno sem vnesel ime prejemnika plačila in ga želim spremeniti v vseh "
"transakcijah. Ali obstaja globalno iskanje/zamenjava?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no global search and replace function in &kmymoney;. Nevertheless, "
"it is easy to change a payee's name: select the Payees View and find the "
"entry with the name you want to change. Click with the &RMB; on the payee, "
"select <guimenuitem>Rename payee</guimenuitem> from the context menu, and "
"enter the new name. Since the transactions only use a reference to the "
"payees record, all transactions now show the new name."
msgstr ""
"V &kmymoney; ni globalne funkcije iskanja in zamenjave. Kljub temu je "
"preprosto spremeniti ime prejemnika plačila: izberite Pogled prejemnikov in "
"poiščite vnos z imenom, ki ga želite spremeniti. Kliknite z &RMB; na "
"prejemniku plačila v kontekstnem meniju izberite <guimenuitem>Preimenuj "
"prejemnika</guimenuitem> in vnesite novo ime. Ker transakcije uporabljajo "
"samo sklic na zapis prejemnikov plačil, vse transakcije zdaj prikazujejo "
"novo ime."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why can't I delete an account?"
msgstr "Zakaj ne morem izbrisati računa?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to delete an account, &kmymoney; can have no other references to "
"it. That means you must delete all transactions from that account or move "
"them to another account. If you still can't delete an account, there may be "
"scheduled transactions referring to that account, which may not be visible "
"in the ledger. You need to delete any future transactions and the schedule "
"itself, or switch them to a different account."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati račun, &kmymoney; ne sme imeti drugih referenc nanj. To "
"pomeni, da morate izbrisati vse transakcije s tega računa ali jih premakniti "
"na drug račun. Če še vedno ne morete izbrisati računa, morda obstajajo "
"načrtovane transakcije, ki se nanašajo na ta račun, ki morda niso vidne v "
"glavni knjigi. Izbrisati morate vse prihodnje transakcije in sam časovni "
"plan ali pa jih preklopiti na drug račun."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export Questions"
msgstr "Vprašanja o uvozu in izvozu"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where do I find some more information about OFX parameters?"
msgstr "Kje najdem več informacij o parametrih OFX?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the web with specific questions can sometimes provide useful "
"results, but there is still one site which might give you more information: "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.ofxhome.com/\">OFX Home</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje po spletu z določenimi vprašanji lahko včasih zagotovi uporabne "
"rezultate, vendar še vedno obstaja eno spletno mesto, ki vam lahko ponudi "
"več informacij: <ulink url=\"https://www.ofxhome.com/\">OFX Home</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: faq.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous questions"
msgstr "Razna vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why is there no translation for 'my' language?"
msgstr "Zakaj ni prevoda za 'moj' jezik?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; uses the &kde; settings for language, so first, make sure that "
"your region and language settings are correct. If they are, the most likely "
"reason is that no one has offered to translate it yet. Translating &kde;/"
"&Qt;-based applications is very simple, and does not require any programming "
"skills. If you would like to translate &kmymoney; into your language, please "
"post a message to the proper <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php"
"\">team mailing list</ulink>. Should you fail to find your language in the "
"list or could not contact the team members please mail directly to the "
"<ulink url=\"mailto:kde-i18n-doc@kde.org\">&kde; translation mailing list</"
"ulink> (<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-i18n-doc"
"\">subscription</ulink> required) and someone will give you the details on "
"how you can easily provide a translation for &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; uporablja nastavitve za jezik &kde;, zato najprej preverite, ali "
"so nastavitve vaše regije in jezika pravilne. Če so, je najverjetnejši "
"razlog v tem, da še nihče ni ponudil prevoda. Prevajanje aplikacij, ki "
"temeljijo na &kde;/&Qt;, je zelo preprosto in ne zahteva programerskih "
"veščin. Če želite prevesti &kmymoney; v vaš jezik, prosimo, objavite "
"sporočilo na ustreznem <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php"
"\">poštnem seznamu ekipe</ulink>. Če svojega jezika ne najdete na seznamu "
"ali ne morete stopiti v stik s člani ekipe, pošljite neposredno na <ulink "
"url=\"mailto:kde-i18n-doc@kde.org\">&kde; poštni seznam prevodov</ulink> "
"(potrebna je <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-i18n-doc"
"\">naročnina</ulink>) in nekdo vam bo dal podrobnosti o tem, kako lahko "
"preprosto zagotovite prevod za &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why did the version number jump from 1.0.5 to 4.5, and what happened to "
"KMyMoney2?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj je številka različice skočila z 1.0.5 na 4.5 in kaj se je zgodilo s "
"KMyMoney2?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The use of KMyMoney2 was a historical legacy from when the project went from "
"&kde; 1 to &kde; 2. To avoid changing the name every time there was a new "
"&kde; version, we decided to stick with &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba KMyMoney2 je bila zgodovinska dediščina, ko je projekt prešel iz "
"&kde; 1 v &kde; 2. Da bi se izognili spreminjanju imena vsakič, ko je bil "
"nov &kde; različici smo se odločili, da ostanemo pri &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first version of &kmymoney; that was considered sufficiently stable was "
"labeled 1.0, even though it ran under &kde; 3. As the project became more "
"closely aligned with &kde; we decided to use the same major release number."
msgstr ""
"Prva različica &kmymoney; ki je veljal za dovolj stabilnega, je bil označen "
"kot 1.0, čeprav je deloval pod &kde; 3. Ko je projekt postal tesneje povezan "
"s &kde; odločili smo se, da uporabimo isto številko glavne izdaje."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I report a bug? How can I request a new feature?"
msgstr "Kako lahko prijavim napako? Kako lahko zahtevam novo funkcijo?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The developers encourage your feedback. See the section on <link linkend="
"\"firsttime.contact\">Contacting the Developers/Reporting Bugs</link>."
msgstr ""
"Razvijalci spodbujajo vaše povratne informacije. Oglejte si razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">Stik z razvijalci/prijava napak</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why isn't there an easy way to print some scheduled transactions, or part of "
"the ledger, or ..."
msgstr ""
"Zakaj ni preprostega načina za tiskanje nekaterih načrtovanih transakcij ali "
"dela glavne knjige ali ..."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look in the <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">Reports</link> section. "
"Many of the reports actually provide an easy way to print thing you can't "
"quite do directly from the ledger or other screens."
msgstr ""
"Poglejte v razdelek <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">Poročila</link>. "
"Mnoga poročila dejansko ponujajo preprost način za tiskanje stvari, ki jih "
"ne morete narediti neposredno iz glavne knjige ali drugih zaslonov."

#~ msgid "5.1.3"
#~ msgstr "5.1.3"
